p></span></li></ul><ul><li><span class="fs7lh1-5"><i>Super Mario Bros. 2</i>, </span></li></ul><ul><li><span class="fs7lh1-5">10 million<sup>[10]</sup></span></li></ul><div><span class="fs7lh1-5"> PredecessorColor TV-GameSuccessorSuper Nintendo Entertainment SystemRelated articlesFamicom Disk System, Famicom 3D System</span></div></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>
